d performance awards  for best relative value fund winner hedge fund journal ucits hedge awards  for best convertible bond hedge fund winner hedge funds review european single manager awards  for best convertible bond hedge fund winner acquisitions international hedge fund awards  for uk convertible bond strategy specialist of the year winner mondo alternatives ucits alternatives fund awards  for best relative value fund  years   ferox capital llp is authorised and regulated by the financial conduct authorityferox capital llp is registered in england and wales registration no oc   st jamess street london swa ne disclosure of commitment to the financial reporting councils stewardship code the code under fca cobs r ferox capital llp the firm is an investment manager based in the united kingdom and authorised and regulated by the financial conduct authority we endeavour to apply our approach on stewardship to all companies that we invest in on behalf of our clients our approach is consistent with the firms overall aims which are to provide good longterm performance to our clients and keeping clients interests paramount the firm monitors all investee companies as part of its general investment policy and approach the firm takes action in line with its investment objectives where its research of publically available information warrants such action however given the nature of our chosen investment strategy this approach does not include active engagement with uk listed investee companies nor do we consider that our clients would expect such engagement   if our investment strategy changes in such a manner that the provisions of the code become relevant the firm will amend this disclosure accordingly pillar  our products hedge funds long only ucits funds long biased funds š  ferox capital llp   home    login    privacy notice    disclaimer    website studio   this website is issued in the united kingdom by ferox capital llp which is authorised and regulated in the co